headline: Exact Sciences and Humana Expand Colorectal Cancer Screening Partnership with Cologuard Plus™ Test
summary: MADISON, Wis., July 31, 2025--Exact Sciences Corp. (NASDAQ: EXAS), a leading provider of cancer screening and diagnostic tests, today announced an expanded partnership with Humana Inc. to enhance access to colorectal cancer (CRC) screening.
